OPPONENT TEAM IS MADE TO ATTACK US AND THE OPPONENT IS SHOT BY OUR GUN
EXPOSURE AND FEEL ON WAR FIELD
AIM ON TARGETS IS PRACTICED USING THE GUNS WITH GREAT ACUCURACY AT INITIAL STAGES TO GET THE KNOWLEDGE OF GUNS BEFORE HANDLING.
RESPONSIBLE QUALITIES ARE CHECKED AND THE PRESENCE OF MIND IS RECORDED.
DIFFUSE OF GUN TECHIQUES ARE  HANDLED BEFORE ON FIELD
EXPERIANCE TO AVOID CONFUSIONS ON PRATICLE SIDE.
